e meaning of what Lacoue-Labarthe terms "literature."  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 4aArea Studies : French Studies. 4aLiterature : Literary Criticism. 4aLiterature : Literary Theory. 4aLiterature : Literature. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / French.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package 2016z978311149098440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438463490423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438463490/original  a978-3-11-149098-4  SUNY Press eBook Package 2016b2016  aGBV-deGruyter-alles